  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is Interesting</strong> is a psychological horror narrative based game with roguelite elements. You are being watched, and you aren't really sure why. Delve through the depths of memory to uncover the mystery behind the gray purgatory you find yourself in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras/f2360d00fe59cddd6bb6077e974b0f2e.avif?t=1745262040\" width=800 height=494 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knowledge-based progression</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While each run of the game will differ, the true progression of the story comes from knowledge gained in previous runs. Only by gathering all of this knowledge can you actually see where the ending of this tale lies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras/651bd590f1e0b9a96632bf0c944f24c2.avif?t=1745262040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras_big/651bd590f1e0b9a96632bf0c944f24c2.avif?t=1745262040 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hidden Stats</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your decisions are tracked throughout the game via stats, and these stats drastically alter the way the game can end. You'll have to experiment with every type of choice in order to see everything the story has to offer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras/fadbd0d8ab1fc4b6c50826e902d20d33.avif?t=1745262040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras_big/fadbd0d8ab1fc4b6c50826e902d20d33.avif?t=1745262040 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Sound</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring a custom soundtrack and uneasy ambience, you'll never feel quite safe roaming the halls of this prison.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is Interesting</strong> is a psychological horror narrative based game with roguelite elements. You are being watched, and you aren't really sure why. Delve through the depths of memory to uncover the mystery behind the gray purgatory you find yourself in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras/f2360d00fe59cddd6bb6077e974b0f2e.avif?t=1745262040\" width=800 height=494 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Knowledge-based progression</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While each run of the game will differ, the true progression of the story comes from knowledge gained in previous runs. Only by gathering all of this knowledge can you actually see where the ending of this tale lies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras/651bd590f1e0b9a96632bf0c944f24c2.avif?t=1745262040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras_big/651bd590f1e0b9a96632bf0c944f24c2.avif?t=1745262040 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hidden Stats</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your decisions are tracked throughout the game via stats, and these stats drastically alter the way the game can end. You'll have to experiment with every type of choice in order to see everything the story has to offer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3640750/extras/fadbd0d8ab1fc4b6c50826e902d20d33.avif?t=1745262040\" data-big-src=https://